<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="mathml.xsl"?><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:pref="http://www.w3.org/2002/Math/preference" pref:renderer="mathplayer-dl"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" /><title>gluQuadricOrientation</title><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets Vsnapshot" /></head><body><div class="refentry"><a id="gluQuadricOrientation"></a><div class="titlepage"></div><div class="refnamediv"><h2>Name</h2><p>gluQuadricOrientation — specify inside/outside orientation for quadrics</p></div><div class="refsynopsisdiv"><h2>C Specification</h2><div class="funcsynopsis"><table border="0" class="funcprototype-table" summary="Function synopsis" style="cellspacing: 0; cellpadding: 0;"><tr><td><code class="funcdef">void <strong class="fsfunc">gluQuadricOrientation</strong>(</code></td><td>GLUquadric* <var class="pdparam">quad</var>, </td></tr><tr><td> </td><td>GLenum <var class="pdparam">orientation</var><code>)</code>;</td></tr></table><div class="funcprototype-spacer"> </div></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="parameters"></a><h2>Parameters</h2><div class="variablelist"><dl class="variablelist"><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>quad</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies the quadrics object (created with <a class="citerefentry" href="gluNewQuadric.xml"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">gluNewQuadric</span></span></a>).
                </p></dd><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>orientation</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies the desired orientation. Valid values are
                    <code class="constant">GLU_OUTSIDE</code> and
                    <code class="constant">GLU_INSIDE</code>.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">gluQuadricOrientation</code> specifies what kind of orientation is desired for quadrics rendered 
            with <em class="parameter"><code>quad</code></em>. The <em class="parameter"><code>orientation</code></em> values are as follows:
        </p><div class="variablelist"><dl class="variablelist"><dt><span class="term"><code class="constant">GLU_OUTSIDE</code> </span></dt><dd><p>
                        Quadrics are drawn with normals pointing outward (the initial value).
                    </p></dd><dt><span class="term"><code class="constant">GLU_INSIDE</code> </span></dt><dd><p>
                        Quadrics are drawn with normals pointing inward.
                    </p></dd></dl></div><p>
            Note that the interpretation of <span class="emphasis"><em>outward</em></span> and <span class="emphasis"><em>inward</em></span> depends on the
            quadric being drawn.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="seealso"></a><h2>See Also</h2><p>
